365
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:40,210
What?

366
00:30:58,240 --> 00:31:00,000
Mom!

367
00:31:00,730 --> 00:31:02,750
You are still here?

368
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:07,980
Where have you been?
Is something wrong?

369
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:09,880
