380
00:31:51,190 --> 00:31:52,550
Here.

381
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:01,840
You said I need to settle some things.

382
00:32:01,840 --> 00:32:03,310
What's this?

383
00:32:03,310 --> 00:32:05,140
