The food's getting cold.

403
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:51,950
When you're stressed,
eating is the best.

404
00:33:53,050 --> 00:33:54,880
Thank you.

405
00:33:57,450 --> 00:34:00,760
Sir, how could such a thing happen?

406
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:03,120
